title: Bug 109350: Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
description: On the query result page, no data is returned. The actual result should be that the output parameter is displayed in the edit data set dialog.
OB: On the query result page, there is no data returned. The actual result should be that the output parameter is displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce the bug, follow these steps:
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database.
2. Verify that the query result has been stored in the output parameter as an object.
